Ron sudah banyak cerita tentangmu.
Kapan ia datang?

143
00:13:02,081 --> 00:13:03,391
Pagi ini.

144
00:13:03,983 --> 00:13:08,343
Anak-anak terbangkan mobil ajaibmu
semalam, pulang pergi ke Surrey.

145
00:13:09,122 --> 00:13:12,141
Sungguh?
Bagaimana jalannya?

146
00:13:12,725 --> 00:13:16,975
Maksudku. Kalian lancang sekali.
Lancang sekali.

147
00:13:18,898 --> 00:13:22,298
Kau pasti tahu banyak
tentang para Muggle, Harry.

148
00:13:22,935 --> 00:13:26,535
Sebenarnya apa kegunaan
bebek karet?

149
00:13:31,611 --> 00:13:34,011
Itu pasti Errol membawa surat.

150
00:13:40,086 --> 00:13:42,546
Jemput dia, Percy.

151
00:13:43,222 --> 00:13:46,062
Errolf
la selalu begitu.

152
00:13:48,094 --> 00:13:51,574
Surat dari Hogwarts.
Mereka juga mengirim untuk Harry.

153
00:13:52,231 --> 00:13:54,921
Dumbledore pasti tahu kau di sini.
latak bisa dibohongi.

154
00:13:55,468 --> 00:13:57,168
Tidak
Buku-buku ini tak murah.

155
00:13:57,570 --> 00:14:01,380
Buku mantra saja harganya mahal!
Kita pasti bisa membelinya.

156
00:14:02,642 --> 00:14:06,392
Hanya satu tempat untuk membeli.
Diagon Alley.

157
00:14:08,114 --> 00:14:09,344
Benar.

158
00:14:09,682 --> 00:14:11,522
Ini, Harry.
Kau duluan, sayang.

159
00:14:11,951 --> 00:14:14,581
Tapi Harry tak pernah pergi
dengan bubuk Floo, Bu.

160
00:14:15,121 --> 00:14:16,021
Bubuk Floo?

161
00:14:16,322 --> 00:14:20,072
Kau pergi dulu, Ron, supaya
Harry bisa melihat caranya. Ya.

162
00:14:21,227 --> 00:14:22,867
Masuklah.

163
00:14:23,663 --> 00:14:24,973
Bagus.

164
00:14:28,668 --> 00:14:30,158
Diagon Alley.

165
00:14:36,409 --> 00:14:39,479
Lihat? Caranya mudah, sayang.
Jangan takut. Ayo.

166
00:14:41,647 --> 00:14:42,727
Ayo.

167
00:14:43,049 --> 00:14:45,858
Masuklah. Bagus.
Awas kepalamu.

168
00:14:46,419 --> 00:14:49,409
Benar. Sekarang ambil
bubuk Floo-nya.

169
00:14:51,391 --> 00:14:53,531
Bagus sekali.

170
00:14:53,993 --> 00:14:57,833
Jangan lupa bicaralah yang
jelas sekali.

171
00:15:00,166 --> 00:15:02,276
Diagonally.

172
00:15:09,041 --> 00:15:11,151
Apa katanya, sayang?!
Diagonally.

173
00:15:11,611 --> 00:15:12,540
Sudah kuduga.

174
00:16:37,697 --> 00:16:43,237
Kau tersasar, Nak?!
Tidak, terima kasih. Aku...

175
00:16:44,170 --> 00:16:48,120
Ikutlah dengan kami.
Kami antar kau pulang.

176
00:16:49,208 --> 00:16:51,257
Tidak. Aku mohon...!
Harry?

177
00:16:51,711 --> 00:16:52,641
Hagrid!

178
00:16:52,945 --> 00:16:55,605
Sedang apa kau di sini?
Ayo.

179
00:17:00,186 --> 00:17:01,416
Knockturn Alley

180
00:17:01,754 --> 00:17:06,384
Kau berantakan. Berkeliaran di
Knockturn Alley? Ini tempat buruk.

181
00:17:07,193 --> 00:17:10,703
Jangan sampai terlihat di sana.
Kau akan dianggap penyihir buangan.

182
00:17:11,364 --> 00:17:13,324
Aku tersasar. Aku...

183
00:17:13,766 --> 00:17:16,376
Tunggu. Kalau begitu apa yang
kaulakukan di sana?

184
00:17:16,903 --> 00:17:21,413
Aku? Aku mencari Pembasmi
Siput-Pemakan-Daging.

185
00:17:22,208 --> 00:17:24,758
Mereka memakani kol-kol sekolah.

186
00:17:30,550 --> 00:17:32,450
Harry. Hagrid.

187
00:17:32,919 --> 00:17:34,149
Halo, Hermione.

188
00:17:34,720 --> 00:17:37,030
Senang sekali bertemu lagi!
Aku juga.

189
00:17:37,990 --> 00:17:40,270
Kacamatamu kenapa?

190
00:17:40,760 --> 00:17:43,280
Oculus Reparo.

191
00:17:47,099 --> 00:17:49,499
Aku harus mengingat mantra itu.

192
00:17:50,002 --> 00:17:53,282
